  "detailed_description": "《一念成仙》是一款以滚轴转动、随机出现、组合增益为基础玩法的，需要您的大局观、明智判断和过人的运气，才能继续修仙的漫漫长路。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935070/extras/e73c08b72f89e522aad265cb1e8135ea.poster.avif?t=1655191112\" width=270 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935070/extras/e73c08b72f89e522aad265cb1e8135ea.webm?t=1655191112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935070/extras/e73c08b72f89e522aad265cb1e8135ea.mp4?t=1655191112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>幸运：每次修炼转动后都能获得随机不同的道具，每次渡劫成功能随机抽取各种强力法宝！所以也许提高增加高品质物品概率是个不错的主意<br></li><li>策略：根据自己已有的道具和法宝，作出当前最合适的选择，才是最优策略<br></li><li>成仙：不断的获取更好更合适的道具和法宝，才能在修炼的道路中砥砺前行</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935070/extras/854abe2894cf32df4035896f7a6c7063.poster.avif?t=1655191112\" width=270 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935070/extras/854abe2894cf32df4035896f7a6c7063.webm?t=1655191112\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1935070/extras/854abe2894cf32df4035896f7a6c7063.mp4?t=1655191112\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
